N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 3 ยง 22.14 - Duplicate of accounts to be submitted

State Regulations

Within five days of the filing in court of an account of
proceedings, two copies of the account certified by a principal officer of the
trust company shall be submitted to the superintendent. Notes
